{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "chunkforge-api-collection",
    "name": "ChunkForge API",
    "description": "Colección para probar ChunkForge API: preparación de documentos y generación de embeddings.\n\n**Flujo:**\n1. Ejecutar Prepare (file o text)\n2. Copiar `document_id` de la respuesta a la variable de entorno `document_id`\n3. Ajustar el body de Generate Embeddings con los chunks editados\n4. Ejecutar Generate Embeddings",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8000"
    },
    {
      "key": "document_id",
      "value": "doc_example"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Documents",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Prepare Document (file)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "file",
                  "type": "file",
                  "src": [],
                  "description": "PDF, DOCX o TXT"
                },
                {
                  "key": "mode",
                  "value": "semantic",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "language",
                  "value": "es",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/documents/prepare",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "documents", "prepare"]
            },
            "description": "Sube un archivo PDF, DOCX o TXT. DeepSeek limpia y divide el documento en chunks semánticos.\n\nTras la respuesta, guarda `document_id` en la variable de entorno."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (json.document_id) {",
                  "        pm.environment.set('document_id', json.document_id);",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('document_id', json.document_id);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Prepare Document (text)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "text",
                  "value": "El negocio acepta pagos por transferencia bancaria y efectivo en caja. Horario de atención: lunes a sábado de 8:00 AM a 10:00 PM. Los pedidos se procesan en 24 a 48 horas hábiles.",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "mode",
                  "value": "semantic",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "language",
                  "value": "es",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "filename",
                  "value": "notas.txt",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/documents/prepare",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "documents", "prepare"]
            },
            "description": "Envía texto plano sin archivo. Útil para pruebas rápidas."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (json.document_id) {",
                  "        pm.environment.set('document_id', json.document_id);",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('document_id', json.document_id);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Generate Embeddings",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"source\": \"manual.pdf\",\n  \"chunks\": [\n    {\n      \"chunk_id\": \"chunk_001\",\n      \"text\": \"Métodos de pago aceptados: transferencia y efectivo.\",\n      \"metadata\": {\n        \"section\": \"Pagos\",\n        \"keywords\": [\"pagos\", \"transferencia\", \"efectivo\"]\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"chunk_id\": \"chunk_002\",\n      \"text\": \"Horario de atención de lunes a sábado de 8 AM a 10 PM.\",\n      \"metadata\": {\n        \"section\": \"Horarios\",\n        \"keywords\": [\"horarios\", \"atención\"]\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/documents/{{document_id}}/embeddings",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "documents", "{{document_id}}", "embeddings"]
            },
            "description": "Genera embeddings locales (384 dimensiones) para chunks aprobados.\n\nRequiere `document_id` de un prepare previo (se auto-guarda si usaste los requests Prepare con tests habilitados).\n\nEdita `chunks` con los textos finales del frontend."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "OpenAPI",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Swagger UI",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/docs",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["docs"]
            },
            "description": "Documentación interactiva Swagger."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "OpenAPI JSON",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/openapi.json",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["openapi.json"]
            },
            "description": "Esquema OpenAPI en JSON."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
